description: This Chainlink VRF common Plezier purrs with a rating of 32, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 64, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, Nine Lives for East, 8 for South, and 1 for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70322-89814-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [64 Votes, Common]
